### 3. Zanaatkarın Siparişe Teklif Vermesi (POST)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quotes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1c3RhQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTc4NTkyLCJleHAiOjE3NzgwNjQ5OTJ9.qDEnbVfcF8SCxvTrHRDN0pzUalCM252nUIuwg117WfA

{
  "orderId": "90e7e233-93e3-417b-a37e-446f3e262550",
  "offeredPrice": 10000.00,
  "estimatedDays": 14
}


### 4. Müşterinin Teklifi Kabul Etmesi (POST)  →  sipariş IN_PROGRESS + escrow holdFunds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quotes/21e9fd6d-ff39-4da4-a868-0ed09b1c544c/accept
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJzZW5hQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTc5MTg2LCJleHAiOjE3NzgwNjU1ODZ9.rbv6DnFPMQnk0LzjSyC8FqmF55pT4T4LvfMYGvACXLI


### 5. Zanaatkarın Siparişi Teslim Etmesi (POST)  →  sipariş DELIVERED
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/d8f63763-ffe6-4034-8ac9-31134a7c1e34/complete
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ1c3RhQGV4YW1wbGUuY29tIiwiaWF0IjoxNzc3OTc4NTkyLCJleHAiOjE3NzgwNjQ5OTJ9.qDEnbVfcF8SCxvTrHRDN0pzUalCM252nUIuwg117WfA


### 6. Ödeme Geçmişini Görme (GET)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/d8f63763-ffe6-4034-8ac9-31134a7c1e34
Authorization: Bearer BURAYA_TOKEN_YAPISTIRIN


### 7. Müşterinin Teslimi Onaylaması (POST)  →  sipariş COMPLETED + escrow releaseFunds
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/d8f63763-ffe6-4034-8ac9-31134a7c1e34/approve
Authorization: Bearer BURAYA_TOKEN_YAPISTIRIN


### 8. Değerlendirme Oluşturma (POST)  →  yalnızca COMPLETED siparişler
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/orders/d8f63763-ffe6-4034-8ac9-31134a7c1e34/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer BURAYA_TOKEN_YAPISTIRIN

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Masa tam istediğim gibi oldu, çok memnun kaldım!"
}
